HB 815 Original 2026 Regular Session Carver
Abstract: Provides for federally insured financial institutions or its duly authorized agent
to receive death certificates.
Present law lists entities that are eligible to receive a death certificate.
Proposed law adds federally insured banks and credit unions as entities eligible to receive
a death certificate.
(Adds R.S. 40:41(C)(1)(k))
